{"tid":771527,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地瘋搶麥當勞巨無霸紀念幣 MacCoin炒貴17倍","createTime":"2018-08-08T04:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T07:30:30.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d66ccba21ab712c32336d207969be2b7e869e1","tid":771527,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T04:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180808/large/a1501a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180808%2Flarge%2Fa1501a.gif&h=c1d7bb29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMacCoin全套有5款，背面設計（右）則一樣。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大型連鎖快餐店麥當勞為慶祝巨無霸50周年，在全球50多個國家發行620萬枚MacCoin代幣，一枚代幣可免費換取一個巨無霸。在中國，MacCoin前日推出不久已出現炒價，全套5枚昨日在淘寶網最高放售2,000元人民幣（下同，約2,260港元）。若以一枚MacCoin等於一個巨無霸（約26港元）的價錢計算，每枚代幣被炒高超過17倍價錢。<br />\n麥當勞上周四（2日）開始，在全球50多個國家的36,000多家餐廳，發行620萬MacCoin，共五款圖案，同步舉行活動的中國（不含港澳台），前日共發行超過100萬枚代幣，每家分店約400個名額。活動周一上午10時半開始，市民只要在指定的麥當勞門市排隊，並為巨無霸唱一句「生日快樂歌」，就能免費獲得一枚MacCoin。客人憑代幣可在全球超過50個國家的麥當勞，免費兌換一個巨無霸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180808/large/a1501b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180808%2Flarge%2Fa1501b.gif&h=4f58bcca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑龍江有麥當勞分店排起換代幣長龍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180808/large/a1501c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180808%2Flarge%2Fa1501c.gif&h=83f2bc54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每枚MacCoin可免費兌換一個巨無霸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180808/large/a1501d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180808%2Flarge%2Fa1501d.gif&h=8937b54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上海有市民排隊時中暑不適。<br />\n<br />\n一套5枚炒價2,260元<br />\n<br />\n因噱頭十足，在前日活動舉行前，各地麥當勞門口已大排長龍，當中有老年人，也有年輕人，更有放暑假的學生一族。內媒報道，由開始派發代幣的短短3小時內，麥當勞已送出全部MacCoin。有市民在烈日當空下等候個多小時，才能成功領取。上海徐家匯有市民不敵戶外高溫，在餐廳門口中暑昏厥。除了個別老人家將代幣換成漢堡包，基本沒有人會兌換，有市民稱：「漢堡包吃了就沒有了，代幣可以收藏一輩子。」有部份市民為集齊全套5枚代幣，全家總動員一齊排隊。<br />\n《蘋果》記者發現，淘寶出現大量MacCoin賣家，售價純屬海鮮價，全套5枚賣599元（約670港元）到2,000元不等，單枚普遍在150元至188元（約169至210港元），全套5枚的價錢最高超過原價17倍。麥當勞中國首席執行官張家茵表示，MacCoin是全球首款用食物作為信用支撐的收藏幣，沒有現金價值，有別比特幣等虛擬貨幣，MacCoin是有實體的。不過，炒賣不是中國人的專利，《蘋果》在拍賣網eBay發現，美國全套MacCoin放售300至15,000港元不等，炒價比中國更誇張。<br />\n■記者廖智廣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180808/large/a1501e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180808%2Flarge%2Fa1501e.gif&h=459db5d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n「巨無霸指數」反映國家幣值<br />\n兩岸要聞 7小時前<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180808/20471198\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180808%2F20471198&d=xTomnt8%2Fnx7TIgb7e0FxbGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=5325166a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180808%2F20471198&h=d6909be9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180808/20471198</a><br />\n<br />\n炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2910a1a82383b9c3b566d4b502227867f4567c3","tid":771527,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T04:34:18.000Z","msg":"遲早又出虛擬代幣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc1309b79aae390302b3004793f65ffefdaa210","tid":771527,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fd821e6bb306a1ed3c65dac49e510a5